                                                    What's your vehicle's Color?
                                                </h1>
                                                <input type="hidden" name="colorId" id="colorId" />
                                                <div class="sc-cHPgQl ioeOCk kirk-autoComplete">
                                                    <div class="sc-kYWVYA DfnDF kirk-textField">
                                                        <div class="kirk-textField-wrapper">
                                                            <input type="text"
                                                                   placeholder="Seltos"
                                                                   name="searchBox"
                                                                   aria-haspopup="listbox"
